:SWISS12.
:FED.
Addendum on payment services
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 5mm
:SWISS10.
:FED.
Introduction
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
This addendum concerns your rights and obligations when using &BANKNAVN.'s
payment services. These may include:
.sp 3mm
.of 3mm
*¤Cash deposited into a payment account
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤Cash withdrawn from a payment account
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤Executing a payment transaction to a payment account, including
executing a credit transaction or a card transaction
.sp 3mm
.of
*¤Money transfer.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The key terms used in this addendum are payment transaction, payment
account, working day and interest date.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Payment transaction
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Actions initiated by a payer or a payee for the purpose of
paying, transferring or withdrawing funds without consideration
for any underlying commitments between the payer and the payee.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Payment account
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A payment account is an account set up for the purpose of executing
payment transactions. An example of a payment account is your operating
account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Working day
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A working day is a day when the payer's or the payee's relevant
provider which is involved in the execution of a payment transaction is
open as is required to execute a payment transaction.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Interest date
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The day from which a payment, disbursement or other transaction affects
the calculation of interest on your account.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Special rules on payment services
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN.'s special terms for payment services apply in addition to
this addendum on payment services. Such terms could, for example, be
&BANKNAVN.'s Dankort rules or online banking agreements.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Executing payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
In order for &BANKNAVN. to be able to execute payment transactions for
you, you must state the branch code and account number of the account
from which the amount is to be withdrawn.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
For domestic money transfers, you must state the branch code and account
number of the account holder to whom the amount is to be transferred.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
For international payment transactions, you must state the IBAN code and
SWIFT code.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When using a joint giro transfer form to make a payment, you must state
the FI joint payment system creditor number.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. considers a payment order executed in accordance with the
uniform identification code stated in the payment order to be executed
correctly.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In order for &BANKNAVN. to be able to execute your payment
orders, sufficient funds must be available in the account in question.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Payment order
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Payment orders can be placed in the following ways:
.sp 3mm
.of 3mm
*¤Through personal appearance in &BANKNAVN.
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤Via online banking
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤By sending a letter to &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.of
.kp off
.kp on
A payment order is considered to be received on the working day when
&BANKNAVN. receives the payment order.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Payment orders received shortly before the end of a working day are
considered to be received on the following working day and will not be
processed until the next working day. You can get more information
about the deadline for receipt of payment orders for processing on the
same day by contacting &BANKNAVN..
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Withdrawing, rejecting and reversing payment orders
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
When &BANKNAVN. has received your payment order, it cannot be withdrawn.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, payment orders for execution at a later date can be withdrawn at
the end of the working day preceding the agreed date at the latest.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you want to withdraw a payment order, you can do so via your online
banking service or by contacting &BANKNAVN.. &BANKNAVN. reserves the
right to charge a fee for withdrawing the order.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If your payment order is rejected due to factual errors, &BANKNAVN. will
notify you of the reason for the rejection and how the error which led to
the rejection can be corrected. &BANKNAVN. reserves the right to charge a
fee for this.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. reserves the right to charge a fee when attempting to reverse
funds for which you have supplied an incorrect ID code.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Maximum execution time
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
A payment order will always be withdrawn from your account on the payment
date you have agreed with &BANKNAVN.. It may take up to three working days
from the time when an amount is withdrawn from your payment account until
the amount is deposited into an account in the payee's bank.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Paper-based payment transactions may take up to four working days to
execute. Such transactions include, for example, giro transfer forms or
forms which you fill in at &BANKNAVN. with a view to completing an
international money transfer.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The same applies if you request &BANKNAVN. (by letter or email) to
complete a money transfer.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If an amount is transferred to your payment account, &BANKNAVN. is
entitled to deduct any fees relating to the transfer from the
transferred amount before the amount is deposited in your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Information about payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If there have been any payment transactions in your payment account
during a month, information about the payments will be available daily
through online banking. &BANKNAVN. may charge a fee for this.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.**************************************************************************
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Information on exchange rates
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN.'s website contains information about the actual exchange
rate or reference rate applied in the event of currency conversion.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may change the exchange rate fixed without notice. Notification
of such changes will be given as soon as possible.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Checking payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
You are obliged to regularly check the movements in your account. If
you discover any transactions which do not match your receipts or
which you believe have not been made by you, you must promptly contact
&BANKNAVN..
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Unauthorised payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If you believe that there have been one or more payment transactions in
your payment account that you have not authorised or made, you must
contact &BANKNAVN. as soon as possible after you have discovered the
unauthorised transaction. When assessing whether you have contacted the
bank in time, we will take into account your duty to regularly review
movements in your account. In any case, &BANKNAVN. must be contacted
within two months of the transaction being posted to your account.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Calculating interest and availability
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
.us Calculating interest on payment account deposits
.br
When making cash deposits into your payment account, the interest date
is the working day following the receipt of the funds.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Calculating interest on payment account withdrawals
.br
When an amount is withdrawn from your payment account, the interest date
is the working day when the amount is withdrawn from your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Availability of amounts transferred
.br
Amounts deposited into your payment account will be available to you
immediately after depositing. However, this does not apply to
non-working days.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Availability of cash payments
.br
When making a cash deposit into your payment account, the amount will be
available to you immediately after receipt.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Fees
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Information about any fees charged by &BANKNAVN. for the use of payment
services can be found on &BANKNAVN.'s price list.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Changes
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. reserves the right to change this addendum and payment
service fees without notice. You will be notified of any such changes
in writing or electronically. You are obliged to notify &BANKNAVN. of
any changes in address or email address, and any failure to do so
resulting in you not being notified of changes will be your
responsibility.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Termination
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If you wish to terminate your payment service agreements, you must do so
in writing at one month's notice.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may terminate your payment service agreements at one month's
notice.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
It is the Danish version of the applicable regulations/provisions that
apply at any and all times.
